* Musica Antiqua Köln{{譯名請求}}（{{le|賴因哈德·戈貝爾|Reinhard Goebel}}）
* La Chapelle Royale{{譯名請求}}（[[菲利浦·赫爾維格|菲利浦·赫爾維格]]）<ref name="wilson">{{cite book|last1=Wilson|first1=Nick|title=The Art of Re-enchantment: Making Early Music in the Modern Age|date=2013|publisher=OUP USA|isbn=9780199939930|page=76|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fWgBAQAAQBAJ&lpg=PA134&dq=The%20Taverner%20Choir%2C%20Consort%20%26%20Players&pg=PA76|accessdate=2018-03-02|language=en}}</ref><ref name="billboard-gardiner">{{cite magazine|last1=Waleson|first1=Heidi|title=Super-conductor: John Eliot Gardiner|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vgcEAAAAMBAJ&lpg=PA46&dq=English%20Baroque%20Soloists%20period%20instruments&pg=PA46|accessdate=2018-03-06|magazine=Billboard|publisher=Nielsen Business Media, Inc.|date=1996-09-07|language=en}}</ref><ref>{{cite journal|last1=Knights|first1=F.|title=A farewell to Musica Antiqua Koln|url=https://archive.org/details/sim_early-music_2013-02_41_1/page/173|journal=Early Music|date=2013-02-01|volume=41|issue=1|pages=173–174|doi=10.1093/em/cas166|language=en|issn=0306-1078}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=Philippe Herreweghe|url=https://www.concertgebouworkest.nl/en/philippe-herreweghe|website=www.concertgebouworkest.nl|publisher=Royal Concertgebouw Orchestra|accessdate=2018-03-06|language=en-EN|archive-date=2021-05-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210515175531/https://www.concertgebouworkest.nl/en/philippe-herreweghe}}</ref>
